<!-- PROJECTS -->

<section>
  <h2>Some Projects</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://x.com/mortalprophet/media" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mortal Prophet</a>: Agentic Art, 2026. A collaborative worldbuilding practice between Second Realm and Iris Dayrise, exploring artifacts, narratives, and synthetic myth through iterative dialogue.</li>
    <li><a href="https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=5255065" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Measuring the Human Experience of AI in the Workplace</a>: Research, 2025. Led a mixed-methods study of 299 workers that found the deeper anxiety around workplace AI is often not replacement, but the loss of agency over how systems are used.</li>
    <li><a href="https://paragraph.com/@epr/primitives-dot-art" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Primitives (PRIM)</a>: Networked Art, 2024. Developed a visual language and onchain framework for encoding emotion, color, and structure so artworks could be explored through their underlying ingredients.</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.notion.so/ericprhodes/Prototype-Personas-1d77e64e2ed0805b8aa5c2fbf91100ab" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AI Proto-Personas</a>: Experiment, 2023. Used AI to generate rich market-research personas while documenting the exact places simulated users break down compared to grounded audience research.</li>
    <li><a href="https://secondrealm.com/6h05t.net/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Society</a>: Speculative Fiction, 2023. Co-created a serialized fiction project with a stack of AI writing tools to test whether generative systems amplify storytelling craft or merely imitate it.</li>
    <li><a href="https://unofficialpunks.secondrealm.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Unofficial Punks</a>: Web3, 2021. Created an NFT project that helped spark the AltPunks movement and pushed remix culture, authorship, and internet-native aesthetics into new territory.</li>
    <li><a href="https://medium.com/secondrealm/introducing-tatr-a-social-liquidity-mining-token-in-the-nft-art-space-1822cc9122f1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">$TATR Social</a>: Protocol, 2020. An early SocialFi experiment designed to reward the circulation and distribution of NFT art through peer-to-peer social engagement.</li>
  </ul>

